// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0464 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 1ec3ca65-93dd-5331-a4fc-f197cae5cb46

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*")
